#. <section class="sutta" id="an11.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an11.2:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 11"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 11"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an11.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Nissayavagga"
msgstr "1. Dependence"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 2. Cetanākaraṇīyasutta → na cetanākaraṇīyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an11.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Cetanākaraṇīyasutta"
msgstr "2. Making a Wish"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:1.1"
msgid "“Sīlavato, bhikkhave, sīlasampannassa na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, an ethical person, who has fulfilled ethical conduct, need not "
"make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:1.2"
msgid "‘avippaṭisāro me uppajjatū’ti."
msgstr "‘May I have no regrets!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ sīlavato sīlasampannassa avippaṭisāro uppajjati."
msgstr "It’s only natural that an ethical person has no regrets."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:2.1"
msgid "Avippaṭisārissa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When you have no regrets you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:2.2"
msgid "‘pāmojjaṃ me uppajjatū’ti."
msgstr "‘May I feel joy!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:2.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ avippaṭisārissa pāmojjaṃ uppajjati."
msgstr "It’s only natural that joy springs up when you have no regrets."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:3.1"
msgid "Pamuditassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When you feel joy you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:3.2"
msgid "‘pīti me uppajjatū’ti."
msgstr "‘May I experience rapture!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:3.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ pamuditassa pīti uppajjati."
msgstr "It’s only natural that rapture arises when you’re joyful."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:4.1"
msgid "Pītimanassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When your mind is full of rapture you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:4.2"
msgid "‘kāyo me passambhatū’ti."
msgstr "‘May my body become tranquil!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:4.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ pītimanassa kāyo passambhati."
msgstr ""
"It’s only natural that your body becomes tranquil when your mind is full of "
"rapture."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:5.1"
msgid "Passaddhakāyassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When your body is tranquil you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:5.2"
msgid "‘sukhaṃ vediyāmī’ti."
msgstr "‘May I feel bliss!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:5.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vediyati."
msgstr "It’s only natural to feel bliss when your body is tranquil."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:6.1"
msgid "Sukhino, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When you feel bliss you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:6.2"
msgid "‘cittaṃ me samādhiyatū’ti."
msgstr "‘May my mind be immersed in samādhi!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:6.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""
"It’s only natural for the mind to become immersed in samādhi when you feel "
"bliss."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.313"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:7.1"
msgid "Samāhitassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When your mind is immersed in samādhi you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:7.2"
msgid "‘yathābhūtaṃ jānāmi passāmī’ti."
msgstr "‘May I truly know and see!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:7.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ samāhito yathābhūtaṃ jānāti passati."
msgstr ""
"It’s only natural to truly know and see when your mind is immersed in "
"samādhi."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:8.1"
msgid "Yathābhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, jānato passato na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When you truly know and see you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:8.2"
msgid "‘nibbindāmī’ti."
msgstr "‘May I grow disillusioned!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:8.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ yathābhūtaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ nibbindati."
msgstr "It’s only natural to grow disillusioned when you truly know and see."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:9.1"
msgid "Nibbinnassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When you’re disillusioned you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:9.2"
msgid "‘virajjāmī’ti."
msgstr "‘May I become dispassionate!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:9.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ nibbinno virajjati."
msgstr "It’s only natural to grow dispassionate when you’re disillusioned."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:10.1"
msgid "Virattassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ:"
msgstr "When you’re dispassionate you need not make a wish:"

msgctxt "an11.2:10.2"
msgid "‘vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ sacchikaromī’ti."
msgstr "‘May I realize the knowledge and vision of freedom!’"

msgctxt "an11.2:10.3"
msgid "Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ viratto vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ sacchikaroti."
msgstr ""
"It’s only natural to realize the knowledge and vision of freedom when you’re "
"dispassionate."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an11.2:11.1"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, bhikkhave, virāgo vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso, "
"nibbidā virāgatthā virāgānisaṃsā, yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ nibbidatthaṃ "
"nibbidānisaṃsaṃ, samādhi yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho "
"yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso, sukhaṃ samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsaṃ, passaddhi "
"sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā, pīti passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā, pāmojjaṃ "
"pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsaṃ, avippaṭisāro pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso, kusalāni "
"sīlāni avippaṭisāratthāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsāni."
msgstr ""
"And so, mendicants, the knowledge and vision of freedom is the purpose and "
"benefit of dispassion. Dispassion is the purpose and benefit of "
"disillusionment. Disillusionment is the purpose and benefit of truly knowing "
"and seeing. Truly knowing and seeing is the purpose and benefit of "
"immersion. Immersion is the purpose and benefit of bliss. Bliss is the "
"purpose and benefit of tranquility. Tranquility is the purpose and benefit "
"of rapture. Rapture is the purpose and benefit of joy. Joy is the purpose "
"and benefit of not having regrets. Not having regrets is the purpose and "
"benefit of skillful ethics."

msgctxt "an11.2:11.2"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, bhikkhave, dhammā dhamme abhisandenti, dhammā dhamme paripūrenti "
"apārā pāraṃ gamanāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"And so, mendicants, good qualities flow on and fill up from one to the "
"other, for going from the near shore to the far shore.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an11.2:11.3"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
